@startuml ThesisManagementAPI-UseCaseDiagram

title Thesis Management API - Use Case Diagram

left to right direction

actor Student
actor Tutor
actor Admin
actor "External Application" as App

rectangle "Thesis Management System" {
    usecase "Login" as UC_LOGIN
    usecase "Search for Tutors by Topic" as UC_SEARCH_TUTORS
    usecase "View Tutor Profile" as UC_VIEW_TUTOR
    
    usecase "View Own Theses" as UC_VIEW_OWN_THESES
    usecase "Create Thesis" as UC_CREATE_THESIS
    
    usecase "View Assigned Theses" as UC_VIEW_ASSIGNED_THESES
    usecase "Update Thesis" as UC_UPDATE_THESIS
    
    usecase "Manage All Users" as UC_MANAGE_USERS
    usecase "Manage All Topics" as UC_MANAGE_TOPICS
    usecase "Manage All Theses" as UC_MANAGE_THESES
}

App --> UC_LOGIN
App --> UC_SEARCH_TUTORS
App --> UC_VIEW_TUTOR

Student -> UC_VIEW_OWN_THESES
Student -> UC_CREATE_THESIS

Tutor -> UC_VIEW_ASSIGNED_THESES
Tutor -> UC_UPDATE_THESIS

Admin -> UC_MANAGE_USERS
Admin -> UC_MANAGE_TOPICS
Admin -> UC_MANAGE_THESES

@enduml
